tech.lity.rea.skatolo.gui.group

Class Tab

  • java.lang.Object
    • tech.lity.rea.skatolo.gui.group.ControllerGroup<Tab>
      • tech.lity.rea.skatolo.gui.group.Tab
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ControlListener, ControllerInterface<Tab>, SkatoloConstants

    public class Tab
extends ControllerGroup<Tab>
    Tabs are used to organize controllers. Tabs are arranged horizontally from the top-left corner by default, Tab extends ControllerGroup, for more available methods see the ControllerGroup documentation. Reposition tabs with skatolo.ControlWindow#setPositionOfTabs(int, int)
